{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_110.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime02","chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Say, Mom...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What is it, Mabayu?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You can see the future, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Sure, if I'm feeling up to it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's so cool!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yep, it's a gift I've been blessed with."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And because of that gift,@I can help everyone."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_111.exp3.json","id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I might be in trouble though,@if I ever lost it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So what happens if you change the future?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_114.exp3.json","id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm, I'm afraid the future can't be changed."},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Why?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, now that's a good question.@I don't even know the answer."},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But it won't change,@no matter how hard you try."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Maybe it's because fate is already@decided from the beginning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201},{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But you're telling fortunes, aren't you?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What do you do if you see@a bad future you can't change?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Telling someone would only@make them feel bad, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes, that's true."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So in times like that, I just@keep it to myself, deep inside."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Deep inside...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll only tell them good things.@That way, we'll both be happy."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Doesn't it hurt?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hm?"},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If your heart is full of bad stuff@you can't talk to anyone about..."},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...then I think it'd start to hurt."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp3.json","id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Holding onto someone's future@can be a painful responsibility."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So it gets tough sometimes."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_114.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But...I take pride in what I do."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The gift of seeing the future@is my very life."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your life...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_111.exp3.json","id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I appreciate your concern though."},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm lucky to have a sweet daughter@like you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":801201}],"textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":833400,"pos":1}]},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime18","chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Huh...?","textAvColorRGB":"255255255"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp3.json","id":833400}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]It can't be..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":833400,"pos":2}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":801201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Mom?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom, what's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":200}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Please, stay away!"},{"chara":[{"id":801201}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What..?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I saw it..."},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I saw it!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21379.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"deleteArmatureList":[1],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":100}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]At that time...@Mom saw my future.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]A future where I would have@witnessed her death."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, if I wasn't there at that time..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom wouldn't have known her fate."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]She wouldn't have suffered@so much in fear of death!"},{"chara":[{"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's because of me that Mom..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":200}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]No, it's not your fault."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I don't need that kind of comfort."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm not trying to comfort you."},{"bgmFadeOut":3000,"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Listen, Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You were your mother's hope."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Hope?"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime21","chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That wasn't the first time@your mother saw her own future."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She had seen it several times before."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Suddenly, she would see the future of@someone nearby, knowing her own fate."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It was unavoidable."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833501,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She could see happy things,@but also sad ones."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Among them, there were futures@where she would lose her loved ones."},{"chara":[{"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ah... Could it be that..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]She saw Dad's future too?"},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes, that's right."},{"chara":[{"id":833501},{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Your mother desperately@tried to change the future."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She tried to prevent the accident@involving your father, but..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She couldn't change it."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She could only watch@her loved ones die."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833501,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That was...the absolute rule@of the futures she could see."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]No way..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]At that time, your mother@sank into despair."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She lashed out at those around her@and cursed her own power."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She wondered what the point of foresight@was if she couldn't change the future."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Living without being able to save@her loved ones had no meaning."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And the one who saved her@from despair..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":833501,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Was you, Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Me...?"},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Your existence in the future was@your mother's reason to live."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Your life itself was the hope@for a dazzling future."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833501,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Her own death would have meant@letting go of her hope..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's why she lost herself@to unbearable pain."},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":200}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's not your fault.@She didn't hate you."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But rather..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She suffered because@she loved you so much."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mom..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But...if that's the case..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If I hadn't been there...if she hadn't@been able to see the future..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu, maybe you don't remember@because the shock was too great."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The doctors said it was the@side effects of chemotherapy, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]In the last days of her life, your mother@seemed to have lost her memory."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh..."},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":2,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21014.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":0,"pos":0,"zOrder":110.0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, Mabayu, welcome.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200906}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mom...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Are you okay...?@Are you not feeling sick?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Not at all. It's as if the@cloudy sky has cleared up."},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm sorry for worrying you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":200}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'll get well soon and become@a healthy mother again!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]M... M-M..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200906}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":400,"pos":1,"posX":-40,"tear":1,"zOrder":100.0}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20][chara:833400:effect_shake][chara:833400:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_051.exp3.json]MOM!!"},{"chara":[{"id":833400,"motion":0},{"id":200906,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Hm? What's wrong?@Why are you crying?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833400,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Hehehe, don't worry.@Because you're a strong girl, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":833400}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu's Mother","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]No matter what fate throws at me,@you're my hope."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21379.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200912,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"deleteArmatureList":[2],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":200912}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]That's right...","textAvColor":"textMabayu","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200912}],"nameAvCenter":"Mabayu","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]I was with Mom in this room,@in her final moments..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200912}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833501,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu, listen."},{"chara":[{"id":200902}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sakie...?"},{"chara":[{"id":833501,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Even if there are hardships,@even if there is suffering..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The people who love you@will always be by your side..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":833501}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Even if they become distant,@even if they fade from memory..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833501,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sakie","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Your presence here is very meaningful."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200902,"tear":1}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Yeah."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
